{"tid":2453250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中俄等17國擬成立捍衛《聯合國憲章》的 “反制裁聯盟”","createTime":"2021-03-19T10:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T11:12:03.000Z","uid":391580,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a7678a4e9d0e722615e1c3580a0868adc71680","tid":2453250,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"據國際法務3月16日消息，中國、俄羅斯、朝鮮、伊朗、委內瑞拉、敘利亞、古巴、白俄羅斯、巴勒斯坦等17個國家計劃在聯合國成立一個名為&ldquo;捍衛《聯合國憲章》之友&rdquo;的聯盟，以反對個別國家奉行單邊主義、在處理國際關系時動輒使用武力或單方面經濟制裁，從而捍衛《聯合國憲章》和國際機構有效性，促進國家間平等對話、寬容和團結。該聯盟由委內瑞拉牽頭而成，共17個國家簽字成為創始成員，近期已向聯合國的所有成員國發送信函，邀請有意願的國家繼續加盟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGS35no.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGS35no.jpg&h=a354a7bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a72294bff2549658a858fa68afe1fe1ec7e9471","tid":2453250,"uid":337336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"共產主義&mdash;&mdash;流氓政權聯盟向西方資本主義偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"ef29e3abd20df370b5f7db42e8e41e8ab1a6fb1c","tid":2453250,"uid":138012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"21st century&rsquo;s axis of evil"},{"pid":"e445dbf8b848a4a54762b08a1895706acda9c9c9","tid":2453250,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"內循環"},{"pid":"64c15089fe1625f92824cbf5e66e614fbf9b51cc","tid":2453250,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"捍衛《聯合國憲章》之友的聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e35b0d70627de807bd8b2a84fba8185eaf6ada","tid":2453250,"uid":129169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"得d垃圾國家圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal